Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They landed on Punk Hazard; an island with two parts, one burning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After forming an alliance with Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy finally encountered Caesar Clown
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,aka the Master who rules the island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but was beaten by his mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Law, too, got taken down by the Navy G-5 base commander - Vergo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you take them away? The children are suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Special Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Bird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gastanet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,--Brownbeard! --What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gastanet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:26.64,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Shaking Up the New World! Caesar's Horrendous Experiment!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:36.49,"Sign",,0,0,0,,IN FRONT OF CAESAR'S LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! It's as solid as rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Open the shutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us back Smo-yan and Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Those creepy creatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They went that way but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about them! Focus on saving Smo-yan and Tashigi-chan now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,An airship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get off, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever go out on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheep-san, give me the candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! I want the candy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My head hurts! Master, give me the candy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you can have it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, go straight back to the Biscuits Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've left plenty of candy in there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go back to my research room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax and enjoy the candies in the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They are very, very delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the room! Show me the way, Mr. Sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this way, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--The Biscuits Room! --I want the candy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what to do, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they're all inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,lock them up securely and don't ever let them get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go back to the room like everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and have that sweet candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go! Do you wanna go back to the lab?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, give me the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Come back to me, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go back to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna go home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I wanna get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold outside and don't you realize what floor you're on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go back to the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Help me, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go get the candy already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl! Go back to the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The candy is in that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you people so scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis and the others were very nice to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I'm not a good child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I didn't listen to you! Bro! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get away from the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! What a pain in the butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:17.27,"Sign",,0,0,0,,THE REMAINS OF THE FIRST AND SECOND LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a whole bunch of cuts and bruises on Sanji-kun's body
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alive thanks to his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with me, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:10:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to save me, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be so disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to save the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just sugar is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,what's taking Caesar so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. I was having coffee and cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd. The cookies are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't serve you any cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I wasn't having cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When does the experiment start, Caesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon. Monet, turn the video on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I wish you had your man
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,under better control, Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw Smoker here, I broke into a cold sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well - he was like a wild dog. He was beyond my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But that'll all change after today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you were quite helpless against Vergo! Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The deal I had with you worked in my favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for letting you stay here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to give my people legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be nice, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you're stronger than me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm the boss of this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want to stay here, I need a little bit of insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning on hurting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this, Trafalgar Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to entrust my dear secretary Monet's heart to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay, Monet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In return,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,let me keep your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we have each other by the balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I shouldn't trust anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you learned it the hard way already but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...Vergo has your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it was impossible even for a man such as yourself to notice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but Monet tactfully transformed herself and followed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you alright?! Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you guys are up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we became good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been saved by your diligent secretary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've been more careful about Monet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing as how the "Master" was so dumb, I didn't care much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! He took your heart and you're still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid can you be, letting him take advantage of your own ability?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Smo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The video is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lucky man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a huge ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is on the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? Where is it? That looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...a candy! It's a huge candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When did they place that Video Transponder Snail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:16:07.52,"Sign",,0,0,0,,VARIOUS PLACES IN THE NEW WORLD UNDERWORLD BROKERS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.83,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting, brokers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:58.92,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,It's going to start soon. The Smilies...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:00.18,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,...that made their way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.24,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,from the Burning Lands separately...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:05.00,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,...will all arrive at this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:07.52,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,central part of the Ice Lands very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When they merge into one another
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and become one big "Smiley" again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiment will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see - Smiley is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...the H₂S poison gas bomb itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...the same one that killed everything on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...four years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,H₂S gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the fact they were growing weaker by the minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,those afflicted with the gas were able to take cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I'm going to do is give Smiley,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the weapon from four years ago, a big "boost."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It will add a new effect to the poison gas
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and the weapon of mass destruction will reach completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:18:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The new weapon that will make its debut today is called...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,..."Land of the Dead"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:07.60,"Sign",,0,0,0,,THE ICE LANDS - THE CENTRAL PART
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we even outrun such monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It finally coalesced into one blob on this side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, what is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What difference does it make now?! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! I see a ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like... a candy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's there underneath it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:52.45,"Sign",,0,0,0,,VEGAPUNK'S DRAGON - SMALL SIZE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, I see a big, gel-like creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's Smiley.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we are going to project Master's video on the fog as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you all have to get out of there. It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with the dragon sled...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a problem! The sled is melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it happen? Is it some kind of chemical reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The dragon escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! One thing after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bit overdramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You all, just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The protective suit won't help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it off and run to the lab now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What? O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the suit off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Master is always right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he has a plan! Do as he says!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope this works right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's image is being projected in the air this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about all that crap! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiley! I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, Smiley?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This brings back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait, Smiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You must obey me! Just as I taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I said "Wait"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a great deal to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...four years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all right! You can eat now! Oh yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's acting funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a big candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy, Smiley.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can stop him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Used in the past to convert Punk Hazard into a land of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar's ultimate poison is unleashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It swallows person after person as it spreads...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...and closes in on the Straw Hats as the island is transformed into a hellish landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Deadliest Weapon of Mass Destruction in History! Land of the Dead!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
